com.sap.spe.pricing.transactiondata

Interface IPricingItemCommon

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IConditionFindingManagerCommon
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IPricingItem, IPricingItemSAPExit, IPricingItemUserExit

    public interface IPricingItemCommon
extends IConditionFindingManagerCommon
    The pricing item contains accumulated pricing information of all pricing conditions and provides methods which are working on all pricing condition of this pricing item.

      • setDynamicReturnValue

        java.lang.String setDynamicReturnValue(java.lang.String key,
                                       java.lang.String value)
        This method can be used to set a key-value pair in the dynamic return container.
        Parameters:
        key - this parameter specifies the unique access key of the key-value-pair. If this parameter is null, no key-value pair will be inserted in the dynamic return container.
        value - this parameter stands for the value of the key-value-pair
        Returns:
        if the dynamic return container contains already a key-value pair with the same key, the old value of this key is returned, otherwise null is returned
